,kcgsart,2012-01-06T07:03Z,"it isn't a virus, and it works 100%.  What you do is you move it to where ever you have AVS4You files installed and then the little key app (the actual patch/crack), you drag the 'register' link onto the key app where it says 'open with 'craking th1s c0de 4 fun'.  Then you select the date and click the panther head.  That's how I did it. "

,DellBust,2012-02-06T04:43Z,"Works fine. Copy downloaded files to AVS4YOU folder containing [ie: C:\Program Files\AVS4YOU\AVSVideoEditor].  Double-click avs4you.all.products.activator.2011.(v1.0)-mpt.exe, enter current date and click the image thingy on the top right corner of the activator box.  That's it.  You're done.  Be sure you first  disconnect your PC from the Internet, and scan you entire hard drive for viruses when done and before reconnecting.  I DID find a trojan, but it could have been there from before. "

,radfear,2012-06-06T02:20Z,"AVG had no problem with it. Works fine. Move to AVS4YOU directory, run it as admin. Pick current date (came up by default), click on right icon. Get the [OK] thingy, you're done."
